            <title><![CDATA[Complete Lost Soul Aside Trophy List—How to Get All Trophies]]></title>
            <link>https://insider-gaming.com/complete-lost-soul-aside-trophy-list-how-to-get-all-trophies/</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/complete-lost-soul-aside-trophy-list%E2%80%94how-to-get-all-trophies.1273692/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
        
<p>Lost Soul Aside is finally approaching its launch after being delayed earlier this year, and the full list of trophies is now available.</p>



<p>Initially set to launch in May, <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/sonys-lost-soul-aside-release-date-delayed/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Lost Soul Aside was delayed in April</a> and pushed back to the end of August. No further delays have occured, however, so it’s almost time to jump right in.</p>



<p>If you’re ready to embark on the quest for full completion by gathering all trophies, we’ve got the complete list for you.</p>



<h2 id="h-all-lost-soul-aside-trophies">All Lost Soul Aside Trophies</h2>



<figure><figcaption>Soul survivor. Image via Ultizero Games</figcaption></figure>



<p><strong>Unlocking all trophies in Lost Soul Aside requires completing the base game, as well as gathering collectables, learning all skins, and crafting all items.</strong></p>



<p>The majority of the Trophies are listed as secret, so they won’t appear unless manually selected in the trophy list, but you’ll soon find the rhythm of which ones are secret and not.</p>



<p>For all the basic trophies, check out the table below.</p>



<figure><table><thead><tr><th data-align="center">Lost Sould Aside Trophy Name</th><th data-align="center">Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-align="center">Genesis of the Stars</td><td data-align="center">Collect all other trophies</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Seleria’s Bestowment</td><td data-align="center">Restore Arena’s power and learn the Greatsword Stance</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Celestial Deer’s Horn</td><td data-align="center">Restore Arena’s power and learn the Poleblade Stance</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Legacy of Lethonix</td><td data-align="center">Restore Arena’s power and learn the Scythe Stance</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Arsenal</td><td data-align="center">Enhance all weapons to the maximum level</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Collector</td><td data-align="center">Collect all trinkets</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Shopaholic</td><td data-align="center">Purchase all key items in the stores</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Pharmacist Certification</td><td data-align="center">Collect all crafting recipes</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Alchemy, or Science?</td><td data-align="center">Craft all items</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Culmination of Progress</td><td data-align="center">Learn all skills</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Dispersed Dimension Novice</td><td data-align="center">Complete the first Dispersed Dimension challenge</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Disperesed Dimension Expert</td><td data-align="center">Complete all Dispered Dimension challenges</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Dispersed Dimension Master</td><td data-align="center">Obtain all Bonus Rewards of Dispersed Dimension challenges</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Ultimate Gifted One</td><td data-align="center">Complete all Boss Rush challenges on Normal difficulty</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Surpassing Seleria</td><td data-align="center">Complete all Boss Rush challenges on Hard difficulty</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Arena in His Prime</td><td data-align="center">Upgrade all Arena Powers to the maximum level</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Gethya’s Approval</td><td data-align="center">Collect all the documents</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<h2 id="h-all-lost-soul-aside-secret-trophies">All Lost Soul Aside Secret Trophies</h2>



<p><strong>The majority of trophies in Lost Soul Aside are listed as secret, so won’t appear automatically, so consider this your spoiler warning.</strong></p>



<p>The secret trophies are mostly progression-related; however, awarded after completing specific points of the campaign. There are a few additional challenges that will require more skill, as you must beat a specified enemy on the hardest difficulty without using any items.</p>



<p>Check out the full list of secret trophies in <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3378960/Lost_Soul_Aside/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Lost Soul Aside</a> below.</p>



<figure><table><thead><tr><th data-align="center">Lost Soul Aside Trophy Name</th><th data-align="center">Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-align="center">A Celebration for the Poor</td><td data-align="center">Complete the Prologue – A Celebration for the Poor</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Oversized Fireworks</td><td data-align="center">Complete the Prologue – Twilight of the Empire</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Prisoner for Millenia</td><td data-align="center">Complete the Prologue – A New Dawn</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Sacrifice, or Cost</td><td data-align="center">Complete the Prologue – The Collapse</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Ancient Guardian</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 1 – Departure</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Flames of Molten Fury</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 1 – Seleria Hall</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Tranquil SkyMirror Lake</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 2 – Beside SkyMirror Lake</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Long-Sealed Divine Palace</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 2 – The Hidden Palace</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Celestial City</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 2 – Aeroflux Dimension</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">The Maple Leaf of Legacy</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 3 – Neverwind Monastery</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">River of Oblivion</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 3 – Lethonix Dimension</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Snowbound Borderland</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 4 – Fourtides Coliseum</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Abandoned Mines</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 4 – Redstone Mines</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Collapsed Royal City</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 4 – Royal Court of Frosthold</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Illusory Sanctum</td><td data-align="center">Complete Chapter 4 – Entropis Dimension</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Lost Soul Aside</td><td data-align="center">Complete your first adventure</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Best-Selling Author Liana!</td><td data-align="center">Complete your adventure on Hard difficulty</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Ultimate Legend</td><td data-align="center">Complete your adventure on Nightmare difficulty</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Sanctified Sword</td><td data-align="center">Defeat Victor on Nightmare difficulty without using any items</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Hot Dance in Hot Spring</td><td data-align="center">Defeat Zana on Nightmare difficulty without using any items</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Cleaving the Cycle</td><td data-align="center">Defeat Aramon on Nightmare difficulty without using any items</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<h2 id="h-how-many-trophies-in-lost-soul-aside">How Many Trophies in Lost Soul Aside?</h2>



<p><strong>There are 38 trophies to collect in Lost Soul Aside, including the illustrious Platinum trophy for collecting all the others.</strong></p>



<p>The majority of the trophies are Bronze tier, with 19 in total, but there are also 15 Silver. As for Gold, there are only three, tied to completing challenges on the hardest difficulty setting.</p>



<p>Are you planning to secure the Platinum trophy in Lost Soul Aside? Let us know in the <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/forum">Insider Gaming forum</a>.</p>



<p>For more trophy guides, check out <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/complete-gears-of-war-reloaded-trophy-list-how-to-get-all-achievements-and-trophies/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">all the trophies in Gears of War: Reloaded</a>, and <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/metal-gear-solid-delta-snake-eater-trophy-list-all-achievement-trophy-differences-in-remake/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">all the trophies in Metal Gear Solid Delta: Snake Eater</a>.</p>
