            <title><![CDATA[Kirby Air Riders Release Date Announced]]></title>
            <link>https://insider-gaming.com/kirby-air-riders-release-date-announced/</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/kirby-air-riders-release-date-announced.1273689/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
        
<p>Nintendo has announced the release date of Kirby Air Riders during a special direct presentation on the game.</p>



<p>A special showcase on August 19 provided a detailed look at the game in a 45-minute presentation, with the main highlight being the reveal of the release date.</p>



<p>Releasing exclusively on Nintendo Switch 2, Kirby Air Riders follows the likes of Mario Kart World and Donkey Kong: Bananza in Switch 2 exclusivity, and is the next big exclusive release for the platform.</p>



<h2 id="h-kirby-air-riders-releases-on-november-20">Kirby Air Riders Releases on November 20</h2>



<figure><figcaption>Coming soon. Image via Nintendo</figcaption></figure>



<p>The release date of November 20 for Kirby Air Riders on <a href="https://www.nintendo.com/en-gb/Games/Nintendo-Switch-2-games/Kirby-Air-Riders-2785805.html?srsltid=AfmBOorGceqV5-BYuUj38j3FmEHGvwjLL3aPtpZjKYhsdjI-4HidXnrj" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Nintendo Switch 2</a> was announced during the showcase, with fans now knowing exactly how much longer they need to wait to dive into the game.</p>



<p>Details shared in the special Nintendo Direct also revealed a stacked roster, including King Dedede, Meta Knight, Bandana Waddle Dee, Chef Kawasaki, each with special abilities and traits.</p>



<p>Several maps were also detailed, showing the variety of environments there are to race through, with single-player and online play both supported.</p>



<figure><p>
<iframe title="Kirby Air Riders Direct – 19/08/2025" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Gn5c4RkoYAc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
</p></figure>



