            <title><![CDATA[Helldivers 2 Collab With Halo ODST Lands With Xbox Launch]]></title>
            <link>https://insider-gaming.com/helldivers-2-collab-with-halo-odst-lands-with-xbox-launch/</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/helldivers-2-collab-with-halo-odst-lands-with-xbox-launch.1273641/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
        
<p>The Helldivers 2 collaboration with Halo ODST is confirmed to arrive on the same day as the Xbox launch in the form of a Legendary Warbond.</p>



<p>Initially released as a PlayStation and PC exclusive in February 2024, Helldivers 2 finally launches on Xbox Series X|S on <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/when-does-helldivers-2-release-on-xbox-exact-release-date-time/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">August 26</a>, alongside a Halo-themed Legendary Warbond.</p>



<p>This marks the first Legendary Warbond to release in Helldivers 2, and while Halo has previously been a Microsoft exclusive, the Legendary Warbond is available on all platforms.</p>



<h2 id="h-helldivers-2-halo-odst-legendary-warbond-launches-august-26">Helldivers 2 Halo ODST Legendary Warbond Launches August 26</h2>



<figure><figcaption>Dropping in hot. Image via Arrowhead</figcaption></figure>



<p>As announced in the <a href="https://blog.playstation.com/2025/08/19/helldivers-2-x-halo-odst-legendary-warbond-arrives-august-26/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">PlayStation blog</a>, the Helldivers 2 x Halo: ODST Legendary Warbond lands on August 26 at 5am PT/1pm BST.</p>



<p>The Warbond is packed full of rewards, with a price of 1500 Super Credits. While Arrowhead notes this is “a step up” from previous Warbond prices, it is “packed with gear worthy of the legend.”</p>



<p>In the Warbond, players can unlock two Armor Sets, three primary weapons and a pistol that Halo fans will instantly recognise, and Mean Green patterns for the FRV, Exo Suit, Shuttle, and Hellpod to provide a true Master Chief-inspired look.</p>



<p>Arrowhead adds that the Legendary Warbond is not compatible with the new Premium Warbond Token launching August 26, included in the <a href="https://discord.com/channels/1042063885789827083/1044696485985517638/1407350534578372649" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Super Citizen Edition</a>, and advise making sure your Super Credits are locked and loaded if you want to unlock the content.</p>



<p>The Helldivers 2 x Halo: ODST collab continues the growing relationship between PlayStation and Xbox, which has seen Microsoft release first-party exclusives on the rival console, while PlayStation has started to reciprocate with Helldivers 2 and Black Myth: Wukong.</p>



<p>Will you be purchasing the Helldivers 2 x Halo: ODST Legendary Warbond? Let us know in the <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/forum/threads/3341/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Insider Gaming forum</a>.</p>



<hr>



<p>For more Helldivers 2, check out all the <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/does-helldivers-2-have-cross-progression/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">details on cross-progression in the game</a>, and take a look at <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/fortnites-new-season-feels-like-we-have-helldivers-at-home-arrowhead-says/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Arrowhead’s assessment of the ongoing Fortnite season</a>.</p>
