            <title><![CDATA[Complete Black Myth: Wukong Xbox Achievements List—How to Get All Gamerscore]]></title>
            <link>https://insider-gaming.com/complete-black-myth-wukong-xbox-achievements-list-how-to-get-all-gamerscore/</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/complete-black-myth-wukong-xbox-achievements-list%E2%80%94how-to-get-all-gamerscore.1273569/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
        
<p>Black Myth: Wukong is finally poised to make a debut on Xbox, which means there are a bunch of achievements to grind towards. Here, we’ve got details of them all.</p>



<p>Releasing on Xbox on <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/black-myth-wukong-coming-to-xbox/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">August 20</a>, albeit <a href="https://insider-gaming.com/is-black-myth-wukong-coming-to-xbox-game-pass/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">not on the Xbox Game Pass service</a>, it’s been a long year of waiting for the title that was previously a PlayStation console timed-exclusive, but there’s still every reason to be excited.</p>



<p>If you’re planning on working your way through Black Myth: Wukong to gather every achievement and secure all the Gamerscore available, we’ve got the complete list for you.</p>



<h2 id="h-all-black-myth-wukong-achievements">All Black Myth: Wukong Achievements</h2>



<figure><figcaption>Finally here. Image via Game Science.</figcaption></figure>



<p><strong>Black Myth: Wukong’s list of achievements will have you ticking off challenges of every type, though the descriptions can be rather mysterious.</strong></p>



<p>Rather than provide a detailed breakdown of the task at hand, <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-GB/games/store/black-myth-wukong/9NWQ1Q1FR0C9" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Black Myth: Wukong</a> keeps its cards close to its chest, with all the achievements having a sort of riddle to solve. Some are easier to crack than others, and some become clearer while playing the game.</p>



<p>The table below has all the achievements in Black Myth: Wukong, excluding the secret achievements (more on those later).</p>



<figure><table><thead><tr><th data-align="center">Black Myth: Wukong Achievement Name</th><th data-align="center">Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-align="center">Home is Behind</td><td data-align="center">The old monkey has told his tale. Onward your must go.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Hammer and Hew</td><td data-align="center">Armed head to toe, dread not the foe.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Brew of Bravery</td><td data-align="center">Fresh brew in an old cask. May it stir a great task!</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Handy and Hardy</td><td data-align="center">A good match calls for a good weapon.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Creative Concoction</td><td data-align="center">Tonics are well and good, but not to be wolfed like food!</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Seeds to Sow</td><td data-align="center">Take more fruit as your plants take root.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Scenic Seeker</td><td data-align="center">The most marvelous places for meditation have all met your gaze.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Full of Forms</td><td data-align="center">Each guise grants a new horizon.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Brews and Barrels</td><td data-align="center">Now you can sate yourself with all the drinks.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">A Curious Collection</td><td data-align="center">Every rare wonder the world can offer, collected and kept.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Medicine Meal</td><td data-align="center">“Here, have it, have it all.”</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Portraits Perfected</td><td data-align="center">Humans, beasts, yaoguais, and the Bodhisattvas. All recorded and noted.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Master of Magic</td><td data-align="center">All spells we know are derived from the same source.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Gourds Gathered</td><td data-align="center">Rare is not the gourd but a friend to drink with. </td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Page Preserver</td><td data-align="center">“All the tattered pages can now be compiled in full.”</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Brewer’s Bounty</td><td data-align="center">A blend for every brew to bring out its best.</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Mantled with Might</td><td data-align="center">Shoes on feet, hat on head, embroidered shirt, Daoist robe—free as can be, doing as you please!</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Staffs and Spears</td><td data-align="center">A walking vault of arms you have become!</td></tr><tr><td data-align="center">Final Fulfillment</td><td data-align="center">Each ordeal paves your path to what you are meant to be.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<h2 id="h-all-black-myth-wukong-secret-achievements">All Black Myth: Wukong Secret Achievements</h2>



<p><strong>The majority of Black Myth: Wukong achievements are secret, and the description won’t show unless manually revealed. Therefore, spoilers follow here.</strong></p>



<p>Unlike many other games, however, revealing the description of the secret achievements doesn’t necessarily make them spoiled, as the riddles will keep you on your toes. </p>



<p>The table below details all the secret achievements in Black Myth: Wukong, riddles and all.</p>



